{"tid":1647914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請鼓掌］香港人的馴服是如何煉成？","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T03:13:21.000Z","uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38eca3a710e8d8f3dff4c6e975f16e0ec512be2b","tid":1647914,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:13:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我們要在節目正式開始前便到達錄影廠，坐在觀眾席上。有一些藝員出來向我們作出基本介紹。<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要的是，觀眾席前面的頂端，有兩個小型燈廂，當它顯示著「<span style=\"color: gold;\">請鼓掌</span>」的燈號，不論節目是否真的有趣，觀眾亦要在攝影機前激烈鼓掌。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.takungpao.com/paper/q/2017/1126/3518739_wap.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.takungpao.com%2Fpaper%2Fq%2F2017%2F1126%2F3518739_wap.html&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=1a19f4c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.takungpao.com/paper/q/2017/1126/3518739_wap.html</a>"}]}